    "description": {
      "zh": "Ultra 5声音抑制器是设计给7.62x51 NATO子弹使用的，但它同时也可卓越发挥多口径抑制器的功能，能够用于多种枪械，在使用NATO 7.62、300 AAC、6.8 SPC、6.5和5.56毫米NATO弹的武器上都具有优异的性能。只能安装在Thunder Beast生产的兼容膛口装置上。",
      "en": "The Ultra 5 sound suppressor is designed for use with 7.62x51 NATO rounds, but also functions as a superb multi-caliber suppressor for multiple hosts, providing excellent performance on 7.62 NATO, .300, 6.8 SPC, 6.5, and 5.56mm NATO. Can only be installed on compatible muzzle devices made by Thunder Beast Arms."
